{"tid":1640745,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(香港抗爭) 美國參議員Rick Scott炮轟ESPN和「迪士尼」奶中共","createTime":"2019-10-09T05:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:41:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5308a7806cb0c6e026341a903230bc562822ae2d","tid":1640745,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吸引更多美國政客出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1181768590518865920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1181768590518865920&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ4OqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=1ba76a2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1181768590518865920&h=8b034068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1181768590518865920</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/xnWHFFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnWHFFT.png&h=40104821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03e504e6e9db5f03bcc89dd8681d1d87b38a7ac2","tid":1640745,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"前因<br />\n（迪士尼係ESPN最大股東）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2941100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2941100&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ4OqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=1edfb5f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2941100&h=53b8dc00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2941100</a><br />\n<br />\nNBA》怕中國？《ESPN》高層下令報導避談香港抗爭<br />\n2019/10/09 10:22<br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕火箭總管莫雷（Daryl Morey）力挺香港抗議行動，後續風波越演越烈，中國官方、贊助商及球迷全面抵制NBA，而現在恐怕連媒體言論自由都受到波及，據悉，《ESPN》高層下令報導該事件不得提起政治議題，而是著重在籃球內容。<br />\n<br />\n《Deadspin》報導，《ESPN》新聞節目資深導播Chuck Salituro發通知給旗下員工，當報導中國與NBA之間的分歧事件，不須討論中國與香港的矛盾關係，及解釋為什麼香港發起抗議活動的原因。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，去年NFL再有球員於比賽前單膝跪地唱國歌，表達有色人種或少數族裔受到的不公平對待，引發美國總統川普不滿，同樣是政治與體育連結的事件，當時《ESPN》高層表示，會致力報導其議題。<br />\n<br />\n只是時間推移到現在中國與NBA之間的關係，起因於莫雷力挺港人爆發民權抗爭時，《ESPN》內部卻希望隻字不提政治內容，外界推估可能是因其與中國《騰訊》在2016年簽約，因商業合作關係不想惹惱對方，《ESPN》才會下令禁止報導香港人抗爭細節。"},{"pid":"0b00a89a60bd5b47ba78107515aead531f0893a1","tid":1640745,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edca741b3eb8d8ab2f48bf4e28494a9fcbc687b","tid":1640745,"uid":6840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"美國佬都要自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b1b1499149313aaaacd2aeb930914e6e697c70","tid":1640745,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4edca741b3eb8d8ab2f48bf4e28494a9fcbc687b","tid":1640745,"uid":6840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"美國佬都要自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"要攪大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94b5094c0f9d14013da8305a2d5ca1cfcc52cfc","tid":1640745,"uid":295124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"Southpark又中"},{"pid":"db33bb02dbabc5e0a71565925884f122841cda28","tid":1640745,"uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f94b5094c0f9d14013da8305a2d5ca1cfcc52cfc","tid":1640745,"uid":295124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"Southpark又中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-0